value_i18n.ar_SA:
Who should attend

Bootcamp sessions are for Liferay partners that fulfill the following job roles and responsibilities:

  • Serve in a Technical Support, Software or Sales Engineering, Developer role or similar
  • Build solutions on top of Liferay platform and/or
  • Support Liferay solutions and/or
  • Create or manage code for the Liferay Platform

Meet partner program requirements

Liferay Solution Partners must maintain the minimum certified headcount by partner level as follows:

  • Silver: 2 Developers
  • Gold: 4 Developers
  • Platinum: 6 Developers

What to expect

  • Learn Liferay best practises and new development paradigm through hands-on exercises
  • Strengthen your team’s skills, gain new understanding, and work closely with Liferay subject matter experts
  • Deep dive into technical topics and participate interactively with your colleagues
  • Ask questions directly to subject matter experts and brainstorm ways to anticipate and support your customers’ needs

​​​​​
